name: pam emerson
text: Why have a phone number listed is you never answer the phone!!!!  Very poor business!!

name: Jack Swan
text: Hard to find this wonderful pizza. They have it.

name: Thomas Holbrook II
text: The pizza was good, and the lady who took my order was attentive and brought it out to me when I was finished filling up the car.

name: Diana Jester
text: Thank goodness I looked at the pizza before leaving the store! The cheese was burnt and the toppings only covered half the pizza with the other half being burnt to the edge of the crust they made it again didn't look any better. Not like the Godfather's Pizza I've known! Not again!

name: jacqueline Hunnicutt
